[src:periodic-background-sync/periodicsyncmanager] The **`PeriodicSyncManager`** interface of the Web Periodic Background Synchronization API provides a way to register tasks to be run in a service worker at periodic intervals with network connectivity.
[src:periodic-background-sync/periodicsyncmanager] These tasks are referred to as periodic background sync requests.
[src:periodic-background-sync/periodicsyncmanager] Access `PeriodicSyncManager` through the `ServiceWorkerRegistration.periodicSync`.
